sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant WebView2
    participant Mermaid.js
    
    User->>App: Type diagram code
    App->>App: Debounce (500ms)
    App->>WebView2: ExecuteScriptAsync
    WebView2->>Mermaid.js: renderPreview(code, options)
    Mermaid.js->>Mermaid.js: Parse & render SVG
    Mermaid.js-->>WebView2: Success/Error
    WebView2-->>App: Result
    App->>User: Update preview + status
    
    User->>App: Click "Export PNG"
    App->>WebView2: ExecuteScriptAsync
    WebView2->>Mermaid.js: renderToPngBase64(code, options)
    Mermaid.js->>Mermaid.js: SVG → Canvas → PNG
    Mermaid.js-->>WebView2: Base64 data URL
    WebView2-->>App: PNG bytes
    App->>User: Save file dialog
    App->>User: Write PNG to disk
